With our comprehensive insurance, the main users of the insured vehicles can drive another car third party only providing at the start of the current insurance term they're #NUM years old or over and have the owner's permission. For full terms and conditions please see page #NUM of your policy booklet which can be found by clicking a href#Link target”blank”herea
